OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSunak promises anti-social 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbehaviour crackdown        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Offenders who engage in anti-social    
OL,6, behaviour will have to do immediate    
OL,7, community work in hi-vis jackets and   
OL,8, jumpsuits under new government plans.  
OL,10,FIt aims to have people repair damage   
OL,11,Fthey cause within 48 hours of being    
OL,12,Fgiven an order, through tasks such as  
OL,13,Fcleaning graffiti.                     
OL,15,FThe pilot, covering 10 areas, will show
OL,16,Fthe public such acts are "quickly and  
OL,17,Fvisibly" punished, Downing Street said.
OL,19,FLabour called the pilot "embarrassing" 
OL,20,Fand the government "out of ideas".     
